Upstream attribution
--------------------

rustyroute is based on and inspired by Eurostat's SeaRoute project:

    https://github.com/eurostat/searoute
    Maven coordinates: eu.europa.ec.eurostat:searoute-core
    Copyright (c) European Union, Eurostat
    Licensed under EUPL-1.2

Eurostat's SeaRoute maritime routing network (graph data derived from
shipping lanes and enriched with AIS data) and its shortest-path
algorithmic approach (Dijkstra over the maritime graph) inform this
project.

Vendored Eurostat SeaRoute / MARNET data
----------------------------------------

This repository vendors the following Eurostat SeaRoute / MARNET
GeoPackage datasets, byte-for-byte and unmodified, under
vendor/eurostat-marnet/:

    marnet_plus_5km.gpkg
    marnet_plus_10km.gpkg
    marnet_plus_20km.gpkg
    marnet_plus_50km.gpkg
    marnet_plus_100km.gpkg

    Source repository: https://github.com/eurostat/searoute
    Source commit:     88a2e568a8e0144d1f5a81c3931a7bc2bcce6901
    Source path:       modules/core/src/main/resources/marnet/
    Copyright (c) European Union, Eurostat
    Licensed under EUPL-1.2

See vendor/eurostat-marnet/README.md for download date, file sizes,
SHA-256 checksums, and the full provenance chain.
